  41,30,"Surely those who say, ‚ÄúOur Lord is God,‚ÄĚ and then remain steadfast, the angels descend upon them,¬†ňĻsaying,ňļ ‚ÄúDo not fear, nor grieve. Rather, rejoice in the good news of Paradise, which you have been promised"
